{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"nonisolated"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"transaction"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"value"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Equatable","preciseIdentifier":"s:SQ"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"transform","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"inout","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction","text":"Transaction","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"},{"text":"\n","kind":"text"}]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"value","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A value to monitor for changes."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"transform","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The transformation to apply to transactions","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"within this view.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A view that wraps this view and applies a transformation to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all transactions used within the view whenever "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"value"},{"type":"text","text":" changes."}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this modifier to change or replace the animation used in a view.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Consider three identical views controlled by a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"button that changes all three simultaneously:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The first view animates rotating the “Rotation” "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" view by 360"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"degrees."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The second uses the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transaction(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" modifier to change the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"animation by adding a delay to the start of the animation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by two seconds and then increases the rotational speed of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"“Rotation\\nModified” "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text"},{"type":"text","text":" view animation by a factor of 2."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The third uses the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transaction(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" modifier to disable animations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"affecting the “Animation\\nReplaced” "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" view."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following code implements these animations:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["struct TransactionExample: View {","    @State var flag = false","","    var body: some View {","        VStack(spacing: 50) {","            HStack(spacing: 30) {","                Text(\"Rotation\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees: flag ? 360 : 0))","","                Text(\"Rotation\\nModified\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees: flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction(value: flag) { t in","                        t.animation =","                            t.animation?.delay(2.0).speed(2)","                    }","","                Text(\"Animation\\nReplaced\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees: flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction(value: flag) { t in","                        t.disableAnimations = true","                    }","            }","","            Button(\"Animate\") {","                withAnimation(.easeIn(duration: 2.0)) {","                    flag.toggle()","                }","            }","        }","    }","}"]}]}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","title":"transaction(value:_:)","roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"transaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"value","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Equatable","preciseIdentifier":"s:SQ","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", (","kind":"text"},{"text":"inout","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Transaction","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"